# Standalone-only mmtorust source list: the CMake build generates its own list
# from the canonical CMake source-of-truth and passes it via --sources, so this
# file is unused there and must not drift in git. Regenerate it for a standalone
# `cargo run -p mmtorust`. (susanSources.txt IS committed — the CMake `susan`
# step reads it and there is no generated equivalent.)
