# Generated crate lib.rs (mmtorust emits these deterministically from the
# crate's module set; copy-if-different, so unchanged = untouched mtime). Not
# tracked: the transpile regenerates them before anything compiles them, and
# .cmake/rust_omc.cmake writes an empty placeholder at configure time (derived
# from THIS list) so a clean checkout's workspace loads before codegen runs.
# Exceptions kept in git: openmodelica_ast / openmodelica_error — bootstrap
# deps of mmtorust itself, compiled before any codegen, so their real source
# must already exist.
